Here's a warm and friendly Christmas card message for your colleague:


---

Dear [Colleague's Name],

Merry Christmas and Happy New Year! I just wanted to take a moment to thank you for your excellent technical skills and the great teamwork we've had this year. Your cooperation and dedication have made working together such a pleasure, and I truly appreciate your efforts in helping us reach our goals.

It’s been fantastic collaborating with you, and I’m looking forward to more successes together in the coming year.

Enjoy the holiday season!

Best wishes,
